Hi Jay,

The Westfalia factory used plywood and linoleum for the floor. My 
westfakia has a 1/8" masonite base with laminate flooring on top. If 
you pick a good brand of flooring you should get many years use from a 
single $25 bundle.

http://www.pottsfamily.ca/westfakia/newfloor.jpg

